by Isabel Smith Staff Writer

The Xavier swim team began its spring schedule on Jan PERIOD  following a hiatus at the conclusion of the fall season PERIOD Both teams last competed at the Cleveland State University Magnus Cup in November PERIOD The womens squad finished third of  teams while the mens team took second of six teams PERIOD

Two Musketeers seniors Rob Van Kirk and Luke Johanns represented the mens team at the ATT Winter Nationals PERIOD The Musketeers returned to action in a threeteam meet against host IUPUI and Ball State PERIOD The womens team defeated both of their competitors while the mens team came in second behind the IUPUI Jaguars PERIOD

Sophomore Paxtyn Drew freshman Becca Titterton freshman Caroline Gaertner and senior Claire Brolsma earned a second place finish in the  medley relay with a time of . pERIOD The squad carried the momentum into the individual events as Xavier swimmers took the top three spots in the  free PERIOD Junior Emily Wagner had the best time with  junior Mackenna Rife was second with . and freshman Jenna Wilkes rounded out the Musketeers at third with . pERIOD Freshman Katie Kerr won the  free in . and junior Taylor Jach followed in second place with . pERIOD

The womens team also found topthree finishes in the  fly with freshman Maggie Kauffeld earning second with . and freshman Annie Cummins taking third place with . pERIOD

The men started the meet with a second place finish in the  medley relay PERIOD Junior Erik Biernat freshman Michael Pettinichi and seniors Knox Hitt and Johanns combined for a . finish PERIOD Xavier began the individual events with junior Nick Straders secondplace finish in the  free with . junior Matt Nephews thirdplace finish in the  back with . and Johanns third place spot in the  free with . pERIOD

The Musketeers kept up a solid performance with freshman Chase Baldwins firstplace spot in the  back in . pERIOD Junior Rodrigo Suriano earned second with . and junior Arthur Smith took fourth with . pERIOD

For her performance in the meet Paxtyn Drew was named Big East Swimmer of the Week by TeamUnify and CollegeSwimming.com PERIOD Both squads will be back in action in the upcoming week PERIOD The Musketeer women travel to Duquesne on Jan PERIOD  to face off against the host team and Ohio PERIOD Both men and women will head to the Butler Invite on Jan PERIOD  to face off against Bellarmine St PERIOD Louis Youngstown State and Butler PERIOD
